      <div class="msgContentFrame">Hey all, since the banks have changed overdrafting rules. As you know your bank will not allow you to overdraft or allow items to be purchased if it puts you in overdraft. Only exception to that rule is checks or monthly payments which are marked as monthly reoccurring payments. Well Id &quot;THINK&quot; FFXI and other mmos would be listed as reoccurring but when I called my bank, they claim FFXI does not bill us like that, its like they run it as a 1 time deal each month.  <br /> <br />Anyone know if FFXI will address that in billing? Or if anyone has called them to get that fixed up? Reason I ask, alot of times Im paid on that due date, which comes in after FFXI bills.. but since the money isnt there RIGHT at that moment. Its declined.. Kinda sucks each month starting to have to reactivate each time just because they dont wanna bill us as a reoccurring transaction. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://www.darkmystics.com" rel="external nofollow" title="www.darkmystics.com"><span style="color:Fuchsia"><b>۩ Sanctuary of the</span> <span style="color:Dodgerblue">Dark Mystics Guild ۩</b></span></a> <br />۞ ~Battle With a Mystic?~ ۞ <br /><span class="sm"><span style="color:Fuchsia">Mysticales</span>/<span style="color:Dodgerblue">Mystaria</span> - Slyph - Elvaan RDM 51 WHM 46 BLM 23 PUP 17 <br /> <br /><span style="color:Yellow">FFXI Ringtones/Wallpaper FREE WAP Portal:</span> <a href="/forum.html?forum=10&amp;mid=111576492150536970&amp;num=13" rel="external" title="ffxi.allakhazam.com/forum.html?forum=10&amp;mid=111576492150536970&amp;num=13"> <br /><span style="color:Springgreen">&gt;&gt;Wap Portal Info&lt;&lt;</span></a></span></div></div>
