      <div class="msgContentFrame">Try talking to a human in your actual bank they should(i.e. if they feel like it) be able to make it work.  Or spam the call centre till you get someone to make it work for you.  I do this when I get an NSF with a 45$ fee.  Talk to one person they say they can't and never could remove the fee.  Call right back and the next person drops the fee like its the only option there ever was.  Its all about manipulating the bureaucracy.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>Ummmmmm</div></div>
