      <div class="msgContentFrame">BoA does give you a choice, 1: Your allowed to have monthly charges (That are listed by the company as reoccurring)  and checks to be processed (accepted) or 2: NO OVERDRAFT PERIOD, Got a check out? Tough, it will be denied and sent back to whoever.  <br /> <br />As for Due dates, yea rent can be in by the 5th, now unless FFXI wants to change due dates for us. ;) Still issue is money I put in the bank is after ffxi tried to take it when it wasnt there, bank would accept it if ffxi lists it as reoccurring monthly which case on that day ffxi charge would be &quot;processing&quot; to the bank, same day money goes into bank, and by the next day, both the deposit and ffxi would be considered &quot;posted&quot; and final. <div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><a href="HTTP://www.darkmystics.com" rel="external nofollow" title="www.darkmystics.com"><span style="color:Fuchsia"><b>۩ Sanctuary of the</span> <span style="color:Dodgerblue">Dark Mystics Guild ۩</b></span></a> <br />۞ ~Battle With a Mystic?~ ۞ <br /><span class="sm"><span style="color:Fuchsia">Mysticales</span>/<span style="color:Dodgerblue">Mystaria</span> - Slyph - Elvaan RDM 51 WHM 46 BLM 23 PUP 17 <br /> <br /><span style="color:Yellow">FFXI Ringtones/Wallpaper FREE WAP Portal:</span> <a href="/forum.html?forum=10&amp;mid=111576492150536970&amp;num=13" rel="external" title="ffxi.allakhazam.com/forum.html?forum=10&amp;mid=111576492150536970&amp;num=13"> <br /><span style="color:Springgreen">&gt;&gt;Wap Portal Info&lt;&lt;</span></a></span></div></div>
